attributes.action: Make Dental Care and Eye Care free for everyone on the NHS
attributes.background: In the UK only people who meet certain criteria are entitled to being exempt from having to pay for dental and eye care costs. However, I believe everyone should be entitled to free dental and eye care. Therefore no one is left out of pocket.
